Title: Jeopardy
Plot: The NCIS team must protect Ziva when a suspect dies while being in custody, and her tactic might be the reason why the person died. The things become much more dangerous when the suspect's brother kidnapps Jenny, and demands the release of his brother in exchange for Jenny, but he has no idea that his brother is dead.
GuestStars: Connor Trinneer, Tamara Taylor, Brian Dietzen, Alex Nesic, Tim Russ, Rodney Scott
